# Surface Detection on Vesuvius CT Volumes

End-to-end data science pipeline for detecting papyrus surfaces in 3D CT scan volumes from the Vesuvius Challenge dataset.

## Objectives
- Understand volumetric CT data and surface labels
- Perform exploratory data analysis (EDA)
- Design a supervised learning pipeline
- Train and compare baseline models
- Analyze errors and model limitations

## Workflow
1. Dataset understanding (3D volumes & masks)
2. Exploratory Data Analysis (EDA)
3. Preprocessing & feature extraction
4. Supervised learning setup
5. Model training & evaluation
6. Error analysis and interpretation
